text: John O'Reilly (born 16 November 1930) is an Australian cricketer. He played seven first-class matches for New South Wales between 1953/54 and 1959/60. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: John O'Reilly (cricketer)
